    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA56">
<l>kāṇak kaḻikātal kaimikkuk kāṭṭiṉā</l>
<l>ṉāṇap paṭumeṉṟā ṉāṇumē – pēṇik</l>
<l>karumālaip poṉmēṉi kāṭṭāmuṉ kāṭṭun</l>
<l>tirumālai naṅka ṭiru.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one exceedingly shows much love in order to see [him],</l>
<l>if one says ‘she is shy’, will she [then] be shy<note xml:lang="en" place="foot">Here -ē has to be interpreted as interrogative particle.</note> before</l>
<l>she reverentially shows black Māl as a golden body,</l>
<l>Śrī who shows us Tirumāl?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
